text.tspan: 4 stars: 4x12 grid, 4 zones for each count operation
One of these two chocolate bars has one more hazelnut than the other.
Each turn, select two zones by dragging on the chocolate bars,
then find out how many nuts they contain.
When you know where the extra hazelnut is, select that square and validate.
To get all the points, find the extra hazelnut in only three turns.
Drag this flag where the extra hazelnut is:
